00:01:19.887 --> 00:01:21.013
Oh no.

3
00:01:22.055 --> 00:01:23.014
Oh. shit!

4
00:02:37.464 --> 00:02:38.632
But you continued up?

5
00:02:40.175 --> 00:02:41.176
With no safety rope.

6
00:02:42.385 --> 00:02:43.428
Correct. Yeah.

7
00:02:48.350 --> 00:02:49.935
Do you know much
about this. Mike?

8
00:02:52.270 --> 00:02:55.524
